body: We all fap but just end up reading it lol, great work

Goddamn I love this series. Great art, great scenes, amazingly developed characters and plot for what could have just been a "wham, bam, thank you ma'am" with multiple chapters featuring the same lass.

I find myself more interested in the relationship between the two of the than the fact its a hentai. Seen worse plots and less developed characters in non-h manga...
Refreshing to see a different girl this time.

Ch. 16 are really good.
Ch. 17 ... wait what? Again? 😂 they got themselves in awkward situation.

Oh well, mild humor. But it's really entertaining. 😏 Keep the good work, ObsoleteZero! 👍
